The paper deals with multi-label learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The focus is on embedding of labels and features, which is a common technique in the field of machine learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with image classification (cs.CV), natural language processing (cs.CL), and information retrieval (cs.IR) as it mentions the use of embedding for capturing intrinsic properties such as local invariance and label correlation. Finally, the paper mentions the use of parametrization, which is a common technique in artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
